episodes.title: Cult Experience in Korea & MORE! ENTREVISTA CON MIS PANAS ft. Marianne (마리안느) (미스 빠나스 인터뷰)
episodes.description:
This is ENTREVISTA CON MIS PANAS in which I enjoy interviewing friends found from all around South Korea to discuss and compare cultural differences, experiences and thoughts about our time here in this fun loving country.
